org.apache.hadoop.registry.server.dns

接口 ServiceRecordProcessor

  • 所有已知实现类:
    ApplicationServiceRecordProcessor, BaseServiceRecordProcessor, ContainerServiceRecordProcessor

    public interface ServiceRecordProcessor
    Manage the processing of service records in order to create DNS records.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      int[] getRecordTypes()
      Return the DNS record types valid for this processor.
      void initTypeToInfoMapping(ServiceRecord serviceRecord)
      Initialize the mapping between DNS record type and record information for the given service record.
      void manageDNSRecords(org.apache.hadoop.registry.server.dns.RegistryDNS.RegistryCommand command)
      Manage the creation and registration of DNS records generated by parsing a service record.

    • 方法详细资料

      • initTypeToInfoMapping

        void initTypeToInfoMapping(ServiceRecord serviceRecord)
                    throws Exception
        Initialize the mapping between DNS record type and record information for the given service record.
        参数:
        serviceRecord - the registry service record.
        抛出:
        Exception - if encountering an error.

      • getRecordTypes

        int[] getRecordTypes()
        Return the DNS record types valid for this processor.
        返回:
        the array of DNS record types.

      • manageDNSRecords

        void manageDNSRecords(org.apache.hadoop.registry.server.dns.RegistryDNS.RegistryCommand command)
               throws IOException
        Manage the creation and registration of DNS records generated by parsing a service record.
        参数:
        command - the DNS registration command object (e.g. add_record, remove record)
        抛出:
        IOException - if the creation or registration generates an issue.
